<item>
  <title>Dr. Howard Gimbel Has Been Appointed to the Order of Canada!</title>
  <link>https://www.gimbeleyecentre.com/blog/dr-howard-gimbel-has-been-appointed-to-the-order-of-canada</link>
  <description>&lt;span&gt;Dr. Howard Gimbel Has Been Appointed to the Order of Canada!&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;div style="background-color: #;"&gt;

    
&lt;div class="gbb-row text-body-para gsc-heading"&gt;
    &lt;div class="bb-inner default paraPad" style="padding: ;margin: "&gt;
&lt;div class="bb-container container "&gt;

            &lt;div class="row row-wrapper"&gt;
                &lt;div class="gsc-column col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12"&gt;
                    &lt;article class="content"&gt;&lt;!--  --&gt;
&lt;div class="site-crumbs"&gt;
&lt;p class="rm-component salacious-crumb" id="salaciousCrumb"&gt;&lt;a class="crumb-go-home" href="https://www.gimbeleyecentre.com/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em class="crumb-sep"&gt;/&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.gimbeleyecentre.com/blog"&gt;Blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em class="crumb-sep"&gt; / &lt;/em&gt;&lt;span class="\"current-crumb-item\""&gt;Dr. Howard Gimbel Has Been Appointed to the Order of Canada!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are so very pleased and excited to announce that the head of our practice, Dr. Howard Gimbel, has been honoured with one of the highest distinctions in the nation. Last December, it was proclaimed that Dr. Gimbel has been named to the Order of Canada. The Governor General of Canada announced 125 new appointments, and our skilled &lt;a href="https://www.gimbeleyecentre.com/doctors/ophthalmologist-gimbel/"&gt;eye surgeon&lt;/a&gt; is one of only six Calgarians on the list.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can view the official &lt;a href="http://www.gg.ca/document.aspx?id=17061" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Order of Canada Appointments announcement here&lt;/a&gt;, which has a breakdown of the appointees and more information on the distinction. Dr. Gimbel is deeply honoured and humbled to be included in this select group of Canadians, and we are extremely proud of him.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more information, or to schedule a consultation for eye care here at Gimbel Eye Centre, please contact us today.&lt;/p&gt;
